40 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">几百年来，<span class="_ _8"></span>人类以为物质最重要，<span class="_ _8"></span>结果问题却层出不穷，<span class="_ _8"></span>最</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2c7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">后不得不回到宗教，回到信仰，这也是一个必然规律。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 y288 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在重新发现心灵、<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls1a">探索心灵的过程中，<span class="_ _b"></span>许多科学家发现，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y8d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">藏传佛教其实是一门高深的心灵科学。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
